<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p><strong><a href="https://donttrip.org" target="_blank">Don't Trip</a></strong> is an itinerary planning application that uses the Google Maps API to provide customized recommendations along a travel route. Developed with a <strong>LEMP stack</strong> (Linux, Nginx, MySQL/MariaDB, PHP), the frontend uses modern Vanilla JavaScript, jQuery, and Bootstrap for a responsive and dynamic user experience.</p>

