<h2 id="features">Features</h2>
<h3>Frontend (Client-Side)</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Search for places along a specified route and add stops as desired.</li>
    <li>Automatic or manual dark/light mode based on user preference and time of day.</li>
    <li>Sorting options with regex to filter places by name or distance.</li>
    <li>Detailed place info pages showing open/closed status, images, address, contact info, and more.</li>
    <li>Search history tracking with options to view count, clear history, or use keywords directly as queries.</li>
    <li>Popular places by state with popularity metrics.</li>
    <li>Keyword and place autofill recommendations for a smoother search experience.</li>
    <li>Responsive directions and map integration.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Backend (Server-Side)</h3>
<ul>
    <li>SSL encryption and automatic HTTP to HTTPS redirects.</li>
    <li>Hashed and salted passwords with secure encryption of sensitive information.</li>
    <li>Two-factor authentication compatible with popular authenticator apps.</li>
    <li>Email confirmation, account recovery, and deletion options.</li>
    <li>Expiring password reset tokens with secure email notifications.</li>
    <li>SQL injection protection with parameterized queries across all backend components.</li>
    <li>Brute-force, XSS, and CSRF attack protection through custom IDS logs.</li>
    <li>Session regeneration and expiration to prevent session hijacking.</li>
    <li>Rate-limiting and throttling on frontend components and backend requests.</li>
    <li>OAuth integrations with Google, Steam, Discord, and others.</li>
    <li>Automatic detection of proxy, VPN, and suspicious IP activity.</li>
    <li>Secure API key and credential storage with PHP-Dot-Env.</li>
</ul>

